name: Princess in the other place
description:
Project for some kanobu 2017 gamejam. Mobile game, where you in a role of royal knight should climb on top of the old tower to rescue princess. This build mainly is for HTML version testing, but anyone can leave his/her suggestions or thoughts about the game in the comments.
Link to the jam page, you can press heart button there if you feel that way - http://gamesjam.org/3139/

CONTROLS : SPACE to jump, A/D to dash in air !
